1. Setting Variables 

You can set variables dynamically in Postman using JavaScript. 

// Set a global variable 
pm.globals.set("globalVar", "value");  

// Set an environment variable  
pm.environment.set("envVar", "value"); 

// Set a collection variable 
pm.collectionVariables.set("collectionVar", "value");


2. Accessing Variables 

Retrieve variables for use in requests or scripts. 

// Get a global variable  
let globalVar = pm.globals.get("globalVar");  

// Get an environment variable  
let envVar = pm.environment.get("envVar");  

 
// Get a collection variable
let collectionVar = pm.collectionVariables.get("collectionVar"); 
